    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_8972-9008",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8972-9008",
      "markText": "如果运动员在体育运动期间任由血糖水平下降，那么将很快出现肌肉分解的情况。",
      "totalCount": 385,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8972&rangeEnd=9008",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8972&rangeEnd=9008"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_14_24981-25083",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "24981-25083",
      "markText": "增加阻力训练，从而为增加肌肉量提供生理性动力（刺激）。在诱导肌肉快速增长方面，低负荷、长时间的阻力训练优于高负荷、短时间的阻力训练[60]。",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=24981&rangeEnd=25083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=24981&rangeEnd=25083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_6069-6108",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "6069-6108",
      "markText": "控制肾上腺素的产生有助于保留肝糖原，而控制皮质醇的产生则有助于保留肌肉蛋白质。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6069&rangeEnd=6108",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6069&rangeEnd=6108"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_559-582",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "559-582",
      "markText": "要知道水果和蔬菜几乎完全是由碳水化合物组成的。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=559&rangeEnd=582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=559&rangeEnd=582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_12718-12833",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "12718-12833",
      "markText": "第2个因素：食用色氨酸含量高的食物（如火鸡或牛奶）后，通过血脑屏障的色氨酸的量会增加，从而导致5—羟色胺的合成量增加，进一步导致过早地出现疲劳[10]。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12718&rangeEnd=12833",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12718&rangeEnd=12833"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_4442-4487",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4442-4487",
      "markText": "胰岛素过多会导致低血糖，进而积累过多的脂肪；胰岛素分泌不足或无效，就会导致高血糖和糖尿病。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4442&rangeEnd=4487",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4442&rangeEnd=4487"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_13_1353-1421",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1353-1421",
      "markText": "血糖（即血液中的葡萄糖）是大脑的主要能量来源。不管肌肉中储备的能量有多少，当血糖浓度降低时，就会发生神经疲劳，而神经疲劳会导致肌肉疲劳。",
      "totalCount": 220,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1353&rangeEnd=1421",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1353&rangeEnd=1421"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_14_7759-7852",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "7759-7852",
      "markText": "那些希望减少体脂的运动员，在训练期间的运动强度应该至少达到最大摄氧量的65%，来增加燃烧的脂肪总量。较低强度的训练会提高脂肪燃烧供能的比例，但是与较高强度的训练相比，燃烧的脂肪总量较少。",
      "totalCount": 220,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7759&rangeEnd=7852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7759&rangeEnd=7852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_12_737-781",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "737-781",
      "markText": "高蛋白、高脂肪和低碳水化合物膳食非常流行，这会对运动员的成绩产生严重的、潜在的负面影响。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=737&rangeEnd=781",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=737&rangeEnd=781"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_12_516-547",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "516-547",
      "markText": "运动强度越高，碳水化合物的供能比例就越大，这一点已经非常明确。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=516&rangeEnd=547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=516&rangeEnd=547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_39_4501-4553",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "4501-4553",
      "markText": "唯一恰当的减重策略是一种轻微的能量不足，而这种轻微的能量不足与一日内能量平衡状态相比，只存在微小的偏差。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=4501&rangeEnd=4553",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=4501&rangeEnd=4553"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_9_1938-1966",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1938-1966",
      "markText": "身体对能量摄入不足的反应是减少体内需要能量的组织的生物量",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1938&rangeEnd=1966",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7a332d8071cc8a0b7a31e96?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1938&rangeEnd=1966"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30181899_9_1848-1911",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1848-1911",
      "markText": "太多的人用饮食来代替运动，希望借此减轻体重。是的，这样做体重很可能会减轻，但是有充分的证据表明，不该损失的身体成分同样减少了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30181899&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1848&rangeEnd=1911",
